Repeater
Repeater allows sending the same request multiple times after modifying it.

Workflow:

Intercept

↓

Send to Repeater

↓

Modify Request

↓

Send

↓

Observe Response

Repeat as many times as needed.

Why Repeater is Important
Instead of refreshing the browser every time,

Burp communicates directly with the server.

This speeds up manual penetration testing.

